{"type": "article", "id": 37533, "title": "Tom Ford 也要卖男士内衣，以及，有一瓶挺浪漫的起泡酒 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-07T03:24:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 4679, "name": "起泡酒"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 1902, "name": "Lady Gaga"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170207104244vNfbeBWktFZ0qcG9.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/tom-ford-mens-underwear-10777409/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tom Ford 扩展男士内衣线</b></a> | 在宣布即将进军奢侈品手表市场的一周之后，Tom Ford 又宣布了他的男士内衣计划。据 wwd 消息称，Tom Ford 此次将与意大利制造商 Albisetti 合作，开设男士内衣支线。这个支线的产品也将同步登陆 Tom Ford 的门店和官网。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/coach-to-showcase-jointly-menswear-and-womenswear-shows/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>纽约时装周上，Coach 也将男女装同台走秀</b></a> | 男女装同台似乎得到了越来越多品牌的青睐，现在，Coach 也加入了进来。此外，Coach 还宣称它将把以往每年四次的走秀日程，压缩至每年两次。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/michael-kors-opens-first-store-in-south-africa-10777172/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Michael Kors 在南非开了第一家店</b></a> | Michael Kors 的南非首家店，开在了开普敦，这家店以出售 MK 的成衣和配件系列为主。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>瑞典袜子品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/han-kjobenhavn-x-happy-socks\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Happy Socks 找来了哥本哈根品牌 Han Kjøbenhavn 合作</a>，推出了一个以汉字元素为主题的系列，还挺有趣的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101318ZorkFex8Mfy9AEVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101328QZsDGcpElBJiYgjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101334Q4xSir2RdpNt6Gvz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在 2 月 26 日东京马拉松正式赛即将开幕之际，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/adidas-adizero-japan-boost-3\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 特别推出东京马拉松专属跑鞋 Adizero Japan BOOST 3</a>。这双鞋款仅在东京发售，以日本国旗的红白配色为主调，鞋舌上印有红色的 TKY 图案，左右后跟也有 TOKYO 2017 字样来呼应主题，与跑鞋一起发售的还有纪念 T-shirt。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101352ibIP4rHDpQq5ORax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667024\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101353n32qf1XkPKighOsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101403owrkt3ODaTJ1VSeQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667033\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101403iCMtxlZQyPHNj2We.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101404DqTBWeRCXzMrgskS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667035\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702071014100InqOe2wRzopag1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">阿根廷起泡酒品牌<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/food/chandon-rose-x-tomoyuki-yonezu/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Chandon，与日本彩妆界的明星设计师米津智之合作，推出了特別包裝的 Chandon Rosé</a>。在这个以“自然美人”为主题的瓶身上，印有米津智之笔下的四季之美，包括樱花、牡丹花、山茶花、鸟类及蝴蝶。这款起泡酒将于 2 月 21 日发售，售价为 3200 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101417SdmUs3WnlvHRXTPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">在超级碗赛事举办期间，首次播出了 Lady Gaga 为 Tiffany&amp;Co 拍摄的传奇风格广告。日前，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/jewelry/lady-gaga-tiffany-co-hardwear-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tiffany&amp;Co 曝光了在广告中出现过的首饰系列 Tiffany HardWear</a>，该系列是 Tiffany&amp;Co 的前创意总监  Francesca Amfitheatrof 为该品牌设计的离别作品，它以“颠覆性的优雅”为主题，灵感来自 Tiffany 在 1971 年创作的中性手链。这个系列将在 4 月 28 日起全球门店同步发售，2 月 5 日开始，可以在美国网站上进行预订。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702071014316xwC2gqm4Ae7MlsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702071014404KTMGlyaPf2v7dn8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101445LjZJNwunbA6YPhs9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101454vWF6TkjRQ2rLnOgK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101454D7PqUfdWCyYzSl5R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101454CPrdnUG918EkXD4h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702071014599E1shcISiVyg6rXN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"NikeLab Essentials 发布 2017 春夏系列 lookbook，以黑、白、橄榄绿为主调，延续了该支线一贯的简约设计。T-shirt 中更是加入了独特的排汗素材 Dri-FIT，大大提升了运动性能。\" rel=\"nofollow\">NikeLab Essentials 发布 2017 春夏系列 lookbook</a>，该系列以黑、白、橄榄绿为主调，延续了该支线一贯的简约设计。T-shirt 中更是加入了独特的排汗素材 Dri-FIT，大大提升了运动性能。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101516s1UP5gozBteHiwJZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101516Y3H29VBCI76cXWzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101516l1WihUaS5JQTy02n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017020710151794JVsh1BvKmGxuk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101517A7EgqZpHVDc2BWkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101517DIgHVQpWmRfv2A5G.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101517BdLGY648mXNpfhZn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702071015187rcfjNlZXk8PO1nC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101518IzcvnQSaGKpyBH6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101516qcGJHz17lBYUOfwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101518hpyzb3QOalnJIvx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101531cZJQM9BjzLxIiUnA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101531TEMlr0ysoCbhLDue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170207101539nyAFwLhIiMG3DX5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/han-kjobenhavn-x-happy-socks\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}